description.undefined: The Prometheus Metric Ontology (PMO) is used to capture information which relates to metric information within the Prometheus monitoring system.

abstract.value: The Prometheus Metric Ontology (PMO) provides a set of classes, properties, and restrictions that can be used to represent and interchange provenance and metadata information relating to Prometheus metric information.
